      "contents": "<div class=\"markitup-box\">\n\t\t\tbanning all news media, putting all dissidents in jail, cancelling all religions, raping all children in the supreme leader's opulent palace.<br/>\nWell, that's what the ideal USSR shall be like that Uncle Stalin told me privately, please don't tell others.\t\t</div>",
